notes: Weapons seizure: As reported on January 1, Counter Terrorism Department (CTD) team recovered 5.5 kg explosives, 30 feet safety fuse, four detonators along with two pistols and 12 bullets near Expressway in Faisalabad city (Faisalabad, Punjab). They also arrested three alleged TTP militants.

notes: On January 1, armed militants attacked a Frontier Corps (FC) training centre in Loralai town (Loralai, Balochistan), resulting in the death of four FC personnel and injuries to two others. In retaliation the FC personnel shot dead four militants.
